- message structure:
    vlin"0.5";vang"0.0";cams"1";    and so on for every variable that need to be sent

- every variable must be 4 char long and the value must be inside double quote [""]

- only the var that need to be updated can be sent

- the order of the vars dosent metter

- once the message is received it's published on a topic "lora", from that topic each node will take the information and act accordingly